    export const updateCheckedV2 = (
    id: string,
    sections: MedicalHistorySection[] | Nil,
    checked: boolean,
    forceUpdate = false,
    ): MedicalHistorySection[] =>
    (sections || []).map((item: MedicalHistorySection) => {
    if (item.section === 'ATTACHMENTS') {
    const { attachments } = item as MedicalHistoryAttachmentsSection
    const newAttachments = attachments.map((attachment) => ({
    ...attachment,
    checked:
    forceUpdate || attachment.id === id ? checked : attachment.checked,
    }))
    const hasCheckedAttachments = attachments
    ? attachments.some((child: EmailEntityConfigSection) => child.checked)
    : false

    return {
    ...item,
    checked:
    forceUpdate || item.id === id
    ? checked
    : attachments?.length
    ? hasCheckedAttachments || item.checked
    : item.checked,
    attachments: newAttachments,
    }
    }

    return {
    ...item,
    checked: forceUpdate || item.id === id ? checked : item.checked,
    }
    })
